ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of International Trade of MARIE-SOLEIL LACOURSIERE of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Vijay Kanwar, whose term has expired.
